flowchart LR
    OCR["OCRResult\nblocks + words"]
    PASS["DE-02\npass-through joiner"]
    REJOIN["DE-03\nline-break rejoin"]
    PUNCT["DE-04\nstray-punctuation drop"]
    SPAN["DE-05\nbbox to span map"]
    LOG["DE-06\nrepair log emitter"]
    NT["NormalizedText\ntext + spans + repair_log"]
    OCR --> PASS
    PASS --> REJOIN
    REJOIN --> PUNCT
    PUNCT --> SPAN
    SPAN --> NT
    REJOIN -.->|RepairLogEntry| LOG
    PUNCT -.->|RepairLogEntry| LOG
    LOG --> NT
